h-speaking Switzerland. Trusted advice, a sharp strategic vision and deep knowledge of the Swiss legal framework.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-[2rem_18rem_1fr] gap-x-10 lg:gap-x-16 gap-y-2 py-10 sm:py-12 border-t border-black/[0.06] items-start sm:items-center\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] text-champagne font-medium select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\">0<!-- -->2</span><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl sm:text-2xl font-light text-navy leading-tight\">Personalized approach</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-muted leading-[1.80] col-start-1 sm:col-start-auto\">Every client is unique. We build a lasting relationship of trust and tailor our solutions to your specific challenges, whatever the size of your organization.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-[2rem_18rem_1fr] gap-x-10 lg:gap-x-16 gap-y-2 py-10 sm:py-12 border-t border-black/[0.06] items-start sm:items-center\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] text-champagne font-medium select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\">0<!-- -->3</span><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl sm:text-2xl font-light text-navy leading-tight\">Absolute confidentiality</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-muted leading-[1.80] col-start-1 sm:col-start-auto\">Discretion is at the heart of our profession. Your data and projects are handled with the utmost care and in strict compliance with professional confidentiality.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-black/[0.06]\"></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-navy relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"navy-grain absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.04]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 container-main py-24 sm:py-32\"><div class=\"flex items-end justify-between pb-10 sm:pb-14 border-b border-white/[0.07]\"><div><span class=\"section-label text-champagne/70\">What we do</span><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-light text-white mt-1 leading-tight\">Our areas<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-champagne\">of expertise</span></h2></div><a class=\"hidden sm:flex items-center gap-2 font-body text-xs text-white/30 hover:text-champagne transition-colors duration-200 shrink-0 ml-8 pb-1\" href=\"/en/services\">View all our services<svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></a></div><div><a class=\"group flex items-center justify-between py-7 sm:py-9 border-b border-white/[0.05] hover:border-champagne/25 transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/en/services/comptabilite-fiscalite\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 sm:gap-12\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.20em] text-white/18 font-medium w-5 shrink-0 select-none group-hover:text-champagne/50 transition-colors duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\">01</span><div><p class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.6rem] font-light text-white group-hover:text-champagne transition-colors duration-300 leading-tight\">Accounting &amp; Tax</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/28 mt-1.5 group-hover:text-white/50 transition-colors duration-300\">Bookkeeping, VAT returns and tax optimization.</p></div></div><div class=\"shrink-0 ml-4\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border border-white/[0.08] flex items-center justify-center text-white/20 group-hover:border-champagne/35 group-hover:text-champagne transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></div></div></a><a class=\"grou