ent</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/28 mt-1.5 group-hover:text-white/50 transition-colors duration-300\">Invoicing, debtor/creditor tracking and company domiciliation.</p></div></div><div class=\"shrink-0 ml-4\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border border-white/[0.08] flex items-center justify-center text-white/20 group-hover:border-champagne/35 group-hover:text-champagne transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center justify-between py-7 sm:py-9 border-b border-white/[0.05] hover:border-champagne/25 transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/en/services/gestion-immobiliere\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 sm:gap-12\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.20em] text-white/18 font-medium w-5 shrink-0 select-none group-hover:text-champagne/50 transition-colors duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\">04</span><div><p class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.6rem] font-light text-white group-hover:text-champagne transition-colors duration-300 leading-tight\">Real Estate Management</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/28 mt-1.5 group-hover:text-white/50 transition-colors duration-300\">Rental management, financial monitoring and legal support.</p></div></div><div class=\"shrink-0 ml-4\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border border-white/[0.08] flex items-center justify-center text-white/20 group-hover:border-champagne/35 group-hover:text-champagne transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></div></div></a></div><div class=\"mt-10 sm:hidden\"><a class=\"btn-outline-dark w-full justify-center\" href=\"/en/services\">View all our services<svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-mineral\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 80\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full pointer-events-none z-0\" style=\"height:var(--slant-h)\"><polygon points=\"0,0 1440,0 0,80\" fill=\"#46184E\"></polygon></svg><div class=\"relative z-10 container-main pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-28 sm:pb-36\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16 sm:mb-20\"><span class=\"section-label\">They trust us</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-navy\">What our clients<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">say</span></h2></div><figure class=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><span class=\"font-display block leading-[0.75] text-gold/[0.13] select-none pointer-events-none -mb-5\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 8rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">“</span><blockquote><p class=\"font-display font-light italic text-xl sm:text-[1.6rem] text-ink/80 leading-[1.62]\">SRD Partners transformed our financial approach. Thanks to their sharp expertise, we significantly optimized our tax burden while gaining clearer visibility into our performance.</p></blockquote><figcaption class=\"mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5\"><div class=\"w-8 h-px bg-gold/45 mb-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold text-navy\">Mr. Durand</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted\">CEO, industrial SME</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"flex items-center gap-5 my-14 sm:my-16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"flex-1 h-px bg-black/[0.07]\"></div><div class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gold/40\"></div><div class=\"flex-1 h-px bg-black/[0.07]\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16\"><figure class=\"flex flex-col gap-5\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-gold/35\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1zm12 0c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg><blockquote><p class=\"font-display font-light italic text-base sm:text-lg text-ink/70 leading-[1.76]\">A responsive, available team with exemplary rigor. Since entrusting them with our accounting, we can fully focus on our core business.</p></blockquote><figcaption class=\"flex items-center gap-3 pt-5 border-t border-black/[0.07]\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.08em] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\">ML</div><div><p class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold text-navy leading-snug\">Ms. Laurent</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted mt-0.5\">Managing Director, services company</p></div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"flex flex-col gap-5\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-gold/35\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1zm12 0c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg><blockquote><p class=\"font-display font-light italic text-base sm:text-lg text-ink/70 leading-[1.76]\">The support during our company formation was impeccable. Helpful and available professionals who anticipated every step with clarity.</p></blockquote><figcaption class=\"flex items-center gap-3 pt-5 border-t border-black/[0.07]\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.08em] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\">FF</div><div><p class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold text-navy leading-snug\">Mr. &amp; Ms. Favre</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted mt-0.5\">Founders, tech start-up</p></div></figcaption></figure></div></div></section><section class=\"relative bg-navy\"><div class=\"hidden md:block\" style=\"height:400vh\"><div class=\"sticky top-0 h-screen flex flex-col overflow-hidden z-20\"><div class=\"container-main text-center pt-28 pb-8 shrink-0\"><span class=\"section-label text-gold/70\">Our approach</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-white mt-2\">A structured<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">partnership</span></h2></div><div class=\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"flex h-full will-change-transform\" style=\"width:400vw;backface-visibility:hidden;-webkit-backface-visibility:hidden\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 px-12 lg:px-20\" style=\"width:100vw\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl w-full\"><p class=\"font-display leading-none text-white/[0.035] select-none -mb-6\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">01</p><h3 class=\"font-body text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-5 leading-[1.2]\">First contact</h3><div class=\"h-px w-10 bg-gold/50 mb-6\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8\">We take the time to understand your situation, goals and constraints. A no-commitment initial meeting lets you present your needs and discover our approach.</p><div><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Deliverables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Initial assessment</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Tailored proposal</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Transparent quote</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 px-12 lg:px-20\" style=\"width:100vw\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl w-full\"><p class=\"font-display leading-none text-white/[0.035] select-none -mb-6\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">02</p><h3 class=\"font-body text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-5 leading-[1.2]\">Analysis &amp; Strategy</h3><div class=\"h-px w-10 bg-gold/50 mb-6\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8\">Our experts thoroughly analyse your financial, tax and administrative situation. Together we define the optimal strategy to achieve your objectives under the best conditions.</p><div><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Deliverables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Analysis report</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Detailed action plan</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Execution timeline</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 px-12 lg:px-20\" style=\"width:100vw\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl w-full\"><p class=\"font-display leading-none text-white/[0.035] select-none -mb-6\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">03</p><h3 class=\"font-body text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-5 leading-[1.2]\">Implementation</h3><div class=\"h-px w-10 bg-gold/50 mb-6\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8\">We execute the action plan with rigour and within agreed deadlines. You receive regular updates and proactive communication at every key stage of the engagement.</p><div><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Deliverables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Compliant files</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Filed declarations</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Interim reports</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 px-12 lg:px-20\" style=\"width:100vw\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl w-full\"><p class=\"font-display leading-none text-white/[0.035] select-none -mb-6\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">04</p><h3 class=\"font-body text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-5 leading-[1.2]\">Ongoing support</h3><div class=\"h-px w-10 bg-gold/50 mb-6\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8\">Our commitment does not end with the initial mandate. We remain your day-to-day partner, available to answer your questions and anticipate changes in your situation.</p><div><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Deliverables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Regulatory monitoring</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Periodic reviews</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Ongoing advice</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"container-main pb-14 mt-14 shrink-0\"><div class=\"flex justify-between mb-8 px-1\"><span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold leading-tight text-center transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-[25%] text-white/95 opacity-100 translate-y-0\" aria-hidden=\"false\">First contact</span><span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold leading-tight text-center transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-[25%] text-white/0 opacity-0 translate-y-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Analysis &amp; Strategy</span><span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold leading-tight text-center transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-[25%] text-white/0 opacity-0 translate-y-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Implementation</span><span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold leading-tight text-center transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-[25%] text-white/0 opacity-0 translate-y-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Ongoing support</span></div><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-px -translate-y-1/2 bg-white/[0.10]\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 h-px -translate-y-1/2 bg-gold/60 transition-all duration-500 ease-out\" style=\"width:0%\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-body font-bold tabular-nums transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-11 h-11 text-[13px] bg-primary-500 text-white shadow-[0_0_0_5px_rgba(48,27,74,0.30)]\">01</div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-body font-bold tabular-nums transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-8 h-8 text-[11px] bg-white/10 text-white/35\">02</div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-body font-bold tabular-nums transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-8 h-8 text-[11px] bg-white/10 text-white/35\">03</div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-body font-bold tabular-nums transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-8 h-8 text-[11px] bg-white/10 text-white/35\">04</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"md:hidden relative z-20 container-main pt-28 pb-16\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><span class=\"section-label text-gold/70\">Our approach</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-white mt-2\">A structured<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">partnership</span></h2></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-[24px] p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0\">01</div><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.08]\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-light text-white mb-3 leading-[1.25]\">First contact</h3><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/40 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-6\">We take the time to understand your situation, goals and constraints. A no-commitment initial meeting lets you present your needs and discover our approach.</p><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Deliverables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Initial assessment</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Tailored proposal</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Transparent quote</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-[24px] p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0\">02</div><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.08]\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-light text-white mb-3 leading-[1.25]\">Analysis &amp; Strategy</h3><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/40 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Our experts thoroughly analyse your financial, tax and administrative situation. Together we define the optimal strategy to achieve your objectives under the best conditions.</p><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Deliverables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Analysis report</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Detailed action plan</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Execution timeline</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-[24px] p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0\">03</div><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.08]\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-light text-white mb-3 leading-[1.25]\">Implementation</h3><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/40 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-6\">We execute the action plan with rigour and within agreed deadlines. You receive regular updates and proactive communication at every key stage of the engagement.</p><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Deliverables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Compliant files</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Filed declarations</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Interim reports</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-[24px] p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0\">04</div><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.08]\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-light text-white mb-3 leading-[1.25]\">Ongoing support</h3><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/40 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Our commitment does not end with the initial mandate. We remain your day-to-day partner, available to answer your questions and anticipate changes in your situation.</p><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Deliverables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Regulatory monitoring</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Periodic reviews</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Ongoing advice</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative bg-cream py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"container-main\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-premium overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"hidden lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[45fr_55fr]\"><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-center bg-primary-50 p-6 xl:p-8 min-h-[480px]\"><div class=\"absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-primary-100 blur-3xl opacity-50\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 w-56 h-56 rounded-full bg-accent-50 blur-3xl opacity-60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 w-full aspect-square flex items-center justify-center\"><img alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-2xl scale-110\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"p-10 xl:p-14 flex flex-col justify-center\"><span class=\"section-label\">Frequently asked questions</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-navy mt-2 mb-3\">Your questions,<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">our answers</span></h2><p class=\"section-subtitle mb-10\">Everything you need to know before entrusting us with your file.</p><div class=\"divide-y divide-gray-100\"><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"true\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-primary-600\"><span>How much does a tax return cost?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-primary-500 bg-primary-500 text-white rotate-45\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:1fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-100\">Our fees depend on the complexity of your tax situation and the type of return involved (individual, company, estate). We systematically provide a transparent quote before any engagement. Feel free to contact us for a no-commitment preliminary meeting.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>What documents do I need to provide?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">The list varies depending on your profile, but generally includes: salary certificates, bank and pension statements, insurance attestations, property deeds and all documents relating to your income and deductions. After an initial discussion, we will send you a precise, personalised list.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>How long does processing take?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">For a standard tax return, allow an average of 2 to 4 weeks after receipt of all documents. More complex cases are subject to a timeline agreed with you in advance. We keep you informed at every key stage of the process.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Can I schedule an appointment?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">Absolutely. We offer in-office meetings in Geneva or Lausanne, as well as video consultations. The first meeting is free of charge and gives you the opportunity to explain your situation at ease. Contact us via our form or by phone to arrange a suitable time.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Is it confidential?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">Confidentiality is a fundamental principle of our profession. All information you share with us is protected by professional secrecy and handled with the utmost discretion. Your data is never shared with third parties without your explicit consent.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:hidden\"><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-center bg-primary-50 py-12 px-8\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary-50\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 w-52 h-52 flex items-center justify-center\"><img alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"260\" height=\"260\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-xl\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"p-7 sm:p-10\"><div class=\"text-center mb-10\"><span class=\"section-label\">Frequently asked questions</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-navy mt-2 mb-3\">Your questions,<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">our answers</span></h2><p class=\"section-subtitle mx-auto text-center\">Everything you need to know before entrusting us with your file.</p></div><div class=\"divide-y divide-gray-100\"><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"true\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-primary-600\"><span>How much does a tax return cost?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-primary-500 bg-primary-500 text-white rotate-45\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:1fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-100\">Our fees depend on the complexity of your tax situation and the type of return involved (individual, company, estate). We systematically provide a transparent quote before any engagement. Feel free to contact us for a no-commitment preliminary meeting.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>What documents do I need to provide?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">The list varies depending on your profile, but generally includes: salary certificates, bank and pension statements, insurance attestations, property deeds and all documents relating to your income and deductions. After an initial discussion, we will send you a precise, personalised list.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>How long does processing take?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">For a standard tax return, allow an average of 2 to 4 weeks after receipt of all documents. More complex cases are subject to a timeline agreed with you in advance. We keep you informed at every key stage of the process.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Can I schedule an appointment?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">Absolutely. We offer in-office meetings in Geneva or Lausanne, as well as video consultations. The first meeting is free of charge and gives you the opportunity to explain your situation at ease. Contact us via our form or by phone to arrange a suitable time.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Is it confidential?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">Confidentiality is a fundamental principle of our profession. All information you share with us is protected by professional secrecy and handled with the utmost discretion. Your data is never shared with third parties without your explicit consent.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"contact\" class=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-stone\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 80\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full pointer-events-none z-0\" style=\"height:var(--slant-h)\"><polygon points=\"0,0 1440,0 1440,80\" fill=\"#F8F9FC\"></polygon></svg><div class=\"relative z-10 container-main pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-28 sm:pb-36\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><span class=\"section-label\">Contact</span><h2 class=\"section-title\">Let&#x27;s talk about your project</h2><p class=\"section-subtitle mx-auto text-center mt-4\">Fill out the form below and we will get back to you within 24 business hours.</p><p class=\"font-body text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.10em] uppercase text-muted/50 mt-4\">Reply within 24 business hours · Confidentiality guaranteed</p></div><form noValidate=\"\" class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-white to-primary-50/25 rounded-2xl border border-primary-100 shadow-premium p-8 sm:p-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-1\"><div><label for=\"name\" class=\"block font-body text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.10em] uppercase font-semibold text-navy/55 mb-2\">Full name *</label><input id=\"name\" type=\"text\" autoComplete=\"name\" placeholder=\"Sophie Dupont\" aria-invalid=\"false\" class=\"w-full font-body text-sm text-ink bg-primary-50/40 border border-primary-200/60 rounded-xl px-4 py-3.5 transition-all duration-200 ease-smooth hover:border-primary-300/80 hover:bg-primary-50/70 placeholder:text-muted/35 focus:outline-none focus:border-gold/50 focus:bg-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/[0.10]\" name=\"name\" value=\"\"/><div class=\"mt-1.5 h-4\" role=\"alert\" aria-live=\"polite\"></div></div><div><label for=\"company\" class=\"block font-body text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.10em] uppercase font-semibold text-navy/55 mb-2\">Company</label><input id=\"company\" type=\"text\" autoComplete=\"organization\" placeholder=\"My Company LLC\" aria-invalid=\"false\" class=\"w-full font-body text-sm text-ink bg-primary-50/40 border border-primary-200/60 rounded-xl px-4 py-3.5 transition-all duration-200 ease-smooth hover:border-primary-300/80 hover:bg-primary-50/70 placeholder:text-muted/35 focus:outline-none focus:border-gold/50 focus:bg-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/[0.10]\" name=\"company\" value=\"\"/><div class=\"mt-1.5 h-4\" role=\"alert\" aria-live=\"polite\"></div></div><div><label for=\"email\" class=\"block font-body text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.10em] uppercase font-semibold text-navy/55 mb-2\">Email address *</label><input id=\"email\" type=\"email\" autoComplete=\"email\" placeholder=\"sophie@example.ch\" aria-invalid=\"false\" class=\"w-full font-body text-sm text-ink bg-primary-50/40 border border-primary-200/60 rounded-xl px-4 py-3.5 transition-all duration-200 ease-smooth hover:border-primary-300/80 hover:bg-primary-50/70 placeholder:text-muted/35 focus:outline-none focus:border-gold/50 focus:bg-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/[0.10]\" name=\"email\" value=\"\"/><div class=\"mt-1.5 h-4\" role=\"alert\" aria-live=\"polite\"></div></div><div><label for=\"phone\" class=\"block font-body text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.10em] uppercase font-semibold text-navy/55 mb-2\">Phone</label><input id=\"phone\" type=\"tel\" autoComplete=\"tel\" placeholder=\"+41 79 000 00 00\" aria-invalid=\"false\" class=\"w-full font-body text-sm text-ink bg-primary-50/40 border border-primary-200/60 rounded-xl px-4 py-3.5 transition-all duration-200 ease-smooth hover:border-primary-300/80 hover:bg-primary-50/70 placeholder:text-muted/35 focus:outline-none focus:border-gold/50 focus:bg-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/[0.10]\" name=\"phone\" value=\"\"/><div class=\"mt-1.5 h-4\" role=\"alert\" aria-live=\"polite\"></div></div><div class=\"sm:col-span-2\"><label for=\"subject\" class=\"block font-body text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.10em] uppercase font-semibold text-navy/55 mb-2\">Subject *</label><div class=\"relative\"><select id=\"subject\" name=\"subject\" aria-invalid=\"false\" class=\"w-full font-body text-sm text-ink bg-primary-50/40 border border-primary-200/60 rounded-xl px-4 py-3.5 transition-all duration-200 ease-smooth hover:border-primary-300/80 hover:bg-primary-50/70 placeholder:text-muted/35 focus:outline-none focus:border-gold/50 focus:bg-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/[0.10] appearance-none pr-10 cursor-pointer text-muted/40\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"\">Select a subject…</option><option value=\"comptabilite\">Accounting &amp; Tax</option><option value=\"conseil\">Management consulting</option><option value=\"audit\">Audit &amp; Review</option><option value=\"patrimoine\">Wealth planning</option><option value=\"creation\">Company formation</option><option value=\"rh\">HR &amp; Payroll</option><option value=\"autre\">Other</option></select><span class=\"pointer-events-none absolute right-3.5 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-muted/45\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"rotate-90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"9 18 15 12 9 6\"></polyline></svg></span></div><div class=\"mt-1.5 h-4\" role=\"alert\" aria-live=\"polite\"></div></div><div class=\"sm:col-span-2\"><label for=\"message\" class=\"block font-body text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.10em] uppercase font-semibold text-navy/55 mb-2\">Message *</label><textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" aria-invalid=\"false\" placeholder=\"Briefly describe your needs…\" class=\"w-full font-body text-sm text-ink bg-primary-50/40 border border-primary-200/60 rounded-xl px-4 py-3.5 transition-all duration-200 ease-smoo