 grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"figure\",\"Ms. Laurent\",{\"className\":\"flex flex-col gap-5\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"svg\",null,{\"width\":20,\"height\":20,\"viewBox\":\"0 0 24 24\",\"fill\":\"currentColor\",\"stroke\":\"none\",\"strokeWidth\":1.5,\"strokeLinecap\":\"round\",\"strokeLinejoin\":\"round\",\"className\":\"text-gold/35\",\"aria-hidden\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"path\",null,{\"d\":\"M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1zm12 0c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"}]}],[\"$\",\"blockquote\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-display font-light italic text-base sm:text-lg text-ink/70 leading-[1.76]\",\"children\":\"A responsive, available team with exemplary rigor. Since entrusting them with our accounting, we can fully focus on our core business.\"}]}],[\"$\",\"figcaption\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-3 pt-5 border-t border-black/[0.07]\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.08em] shrink-0\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\",\"children\":\"ML\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-body text-sm font-semibold text-navy leading-snug\",\"children\":\"Ms. Laurent\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-body text-xs text-muted mt-0.5\",\"children\":\"Managing Director, services company\"}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"figure\",\"Mr. & Ms. Favre\",{\"className\":\"flex flex-col gap-5\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"svg\",null,{\"width\":20,\"height\":20,\"viewBox\":\"0 0 24 24\",\"fill\":\"currentColor\",\"stroke\":\"none\",\"strokeWidth\":1.5,\"strokeLinecap\":\"round\",\"strokeLinejoin\":\"round\",\"className\":\"text-gold/35\",\"aria-hidden\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"path\",null,{\"d\":\"M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1zm12 0c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"}]}],\"$L24\",\"$L25\"]}]]}]]}]]}]\n1c:[\"$\",\"$L26\",null,{\"t\":{\"overline\":\"Our approach\",\"titleMain\":\"A structured\",\"titleAccent\":\"partnership\",\"deliverablesLabel\":\"Deliverables\",\"steps\":[{\"number\":\"01\",\"title\":\"First contact\",\"description\":\"We take the time to understand your situation, goals and constraints. A no-commitment initial meeting lets you present your needs and discover our approach.\",\"deliverables\":[\"Initial assessment\",\"Tailored proposal\",\"Transparent quote\"]},{\"number\":\"02\",\"title\":\"Analysis & Strategy\",\"description\":\"Our experts thoroughly analyse your financial, tax and administrative situation. Together we define the optimal strategy to achieve your objectives under the best conditions.\",\"deliverables\":[\"Analysis report\",\"Detailed action plan\",\"Execution timeline\"]},{\"number\":\"03\",\"title\":\"Implementation\",\"description\":\"We execute the action plan with rigour and within agreed deadlines. You receive regular updates and proactive communication at every key stage of the engagement.\",\"deliverables\":[\"Compliant files\",\"Filed declarations\",\"Interim reports\"]},{\"number\":\"04\",\"title\":\"Ongoing support\",\"description\":\"Our commitment does not end with the initial mandate. We remain your day-to-day partner, available to answer your questions and anticipate changes in your situation.\",\"deliverables\":[\"Regulatory monitoring\",\"Periodic reviews\",\"Ongoing advice\"]}]},\"slantFill\":\"#D2C9D6\"}]\n1d:[\"$\",\"$L27\",null,{\"t\":{\"overline\":\"Frequently asked questions\",\"titleMain\":\"Your questions,\",\"titleAccent\":\"our answers\",\"subtitle\":\"Everything you need to know before entrusting us with your file.\",\"items\":[{\"question\":\"How much does a tax return cost?\",\"answer\":\"Our fees depend on the complexity of your tax situation and the type of return involved (individual, company, estate). We systematically provide a transparent quote before any engagement. Feel free to contact us for a no-commitment preliminary meeting.\"},{\"question\":\"What documents do I need to provide?\",\"answer\":\"The list varies depending on your profile, but generally includes: salary certificates, bank and pension statements, insurance attestations, property deeds and all documents relating to your income and deductions. After an initial discussion, we will send you a precise, personalised list.\"},{\"question\":\"How long does processing take?\",\"answer\":\"For a standard tax return, allow an average of 2 to 4 weeks after receipt of all documents. More complex cases are subject to a timeline agreed with you in advance. We keep you informed at every key stage of the process.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I schedule an appointment?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. We offer in-office meetings in Geneva or Lausanne, as well as video consultations. The first meeting is free of charge and gives you the opportunity to explain your situation at ease. Contact us via our form or by phone to arrange a suitable time.\"},{\"question\":\"Is it confidential?\",\"answer\":\"Confidentiality is a fundamental principle of our profession. All information you share with us is protected by professional secrecy and handled with the utmost discretion. Your data is never shared with third parties without your explicit consent.\"}]}}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"$L28\",null,{\"bg\":\"stone\",\"slant\":\"left\",\"slantFill\":\"#F8F9FC\",\"t\":{\"overline\":\"Contact\",\"title\":\"Let's talk about your project\",\"subtitle\":\"Fill out the form below and we will get back to you within 24 business hours.\",\"trustLine\":\"Reply within 24 business hours · Confidentiality guarantee